---
import Button from '../../ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="brand-led-seo snap-section animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="left-column">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="main-title">
            BRAND-DRIVEN<br>
            SEO
          </h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="highlight-text">
          <p>VISIBILIDADE QUE SUPERA O IMPONDERÁVEL</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-body">
          <p>Quando ativada por estratégias científicas e executada com excelência técnica, sua comunicação digital se torna imã para vendas — enquanto você se concentra no seu negócio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="right-column">
        <div class="secondary-content">
          <h3 class="secondary-title">SEO À PROVA DE FUTURO</h3>
          
          <div class="text-body">
            <p>Abordagens tradicionais se concentram em algoritmos, tornando-se obsoletas a cada atualização e sujeitando sua presença online a oscilações constantes de desempenho.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-body">
            <p>Nosso método se baseia no seu cliente e na personalidade da sua empresa. Não em códigos que ninguém controla.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="cta-container">
            <Button href="#" variant="secondary">
              Conheça a metodologia
              <span class="arrow">→</span>
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .brand-led-seo {
    height: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    position: relative;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 12rem 2rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .main-title {
    font-family: var(--font-family-heading);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
    line-height: 1;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .highlight-text {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .highlight-text p {
    font-family: var(--font-family-primary);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }

  .secondary-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    text-align: left;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .secondary-title {
    font-family: var(--font-family-primary);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .paragraph {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .paragraph:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .paragraph p {
    font-family: var(--font-family-primary);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta-container {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-2xl);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-family-primary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wider);
    border-radius: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-link::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    transition: left 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .cta-link:hover::before {
    left: 0;
  }

  .cta-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(192, 178, 131, 0.3);
  }

  .arrow {
    margin-left: var(--space-sm);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-link:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  /* Animações de entrada */
  .section-header {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .highlight-text {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .description {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .secondary-content {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.8s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Centralização dos elementos */
  .left-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .right-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Responsividade */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .brand-led-seo {
      padding: 10rem 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .section-header {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .highlight-text {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .divider {
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .brand-led-seo {
      padding: 8rem 1.5rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0; 
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      justify-items: center;
    }
    
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .divider {
      align-self: center;
    }
    
    .highlight-text {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .secondary-content {
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .secondary-title {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .paragraph {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .highlight-text p {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
      font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    }
    
    .left-column {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .right-column {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .brand-led-seo {
      padding: 6rem 1rem;
      min-height: 132vh;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    
    .section-header {
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .divider {
      width: 50px;
      height: 2px;
    }
    
    .highlight-text {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .secondary-content {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .cta-container {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .main-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    }
    
    .secondary-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    }
    
    .paragraph {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
